cleaned_text: I established my clinic Wholistic Analysis Services in 1999 with the aim of teaching people how they can achieve and attain good health by: - taking the right nutrients and supplement support for their health - making better choices with their diet and lifestyle - balancing their emotional, mental and physical state to achieve the most out of life The people who attend my clinic are amazed when they find out what is really going on with their health. Amazed at the accuracy of the skills and techniques in determining their state of health. Find my services educational and relevant to their needs
